# ─── SCF licensed catalogue content — NEVER commit ───────────────────────────
# SCF control content is licensed (CC BY-ND 4.0 + a separate commercial licence) and
# MUST NOT be redistributed in this open-source repo. These files are GENERATED at install
# time from the operator's own SCF Excel workbook by the catalogue importer
# (scripts/extract_scf_data.py → docker compose --profile init run --rm catalog-importer).
# Bring your own SCF catalogue; do not check these in.
